kdebase-runtime (4:3.97.0-2) experimental; urgency=low

  +++ Changes by Armin Berres:

  * Replace the meta-package kdebase-workspace with the former content of the
    now removed kdebase-runtime-bin.
  * Add "-Wl,-z" to LDFLAGS to fail if there are missing symbols.

  +++ Changes by Fathi Boudra:

  * Use DEB_CMAKE_EXTRA_FLAGS, CMAKE_SHARED_LINKER_FLAGS and
    CMAKE_MODULE_LINKER_FLAGS.
    It will be easier to move to our cdbs classes whenever we want.
  * Add defs to LDFLAGS.

 -- Debian Qt/KDE Maintainers <debian-qt-kde@lists.debian.org>  Fri, 14 Dec 2007 23:34:02 +0100

kdebase-runtime (4:3.97.0-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
    - Bump build-dep to >=4:3.97.0.
    - Add epoch to kdepimlibs build-dep.
    - Update *.install files.
  * Update Standards-Version to 3.7.3.
  * khelpenter still needs htdig, add Depends on it.
  * Add export LDFLAGS+="-Wl,--as-needed" in rules to make dpkg-shlibdeps
    happier. 

